  <h2>Description</h2>
  <p>Ramen is a Japanese noodle soup with endless flavor variations. This recipe is a quick version with rich broth and fresh toppings.</p>

  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Ramen noodles</li>
    <li>Chicken broth</li>
    <li>Soft-boiled egg</li>
    <li>Sliced pork</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Steps</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Prepare broth in a large pot.</li>
    <li>Cook noodles according to package instructions.</li>
    <li>Assemble bowl with noodles, broth, and toppings.</li>
  </ol>
